JSLint Reporter
Node.js wrapper for JSLint


Usage:
  $ node wrapper.js [options] <filepath>

(requires `make jslint` to generate jslint.js alongside wrapper.js)


Options:

  --<name>
    names as per http://www.jslint.com/lint.html#options (e.g. "--strict")

  --goodparts
    shortcut for recommended options


Using Douglas Crockford's JSLint (http://jslint.com).
